Course Highlights

What is WordPress?

WordPress is one of the most popular CMS these days which is being used for developing websites and blogs. It is highly customized content management system. The main WordPress concepts include a menu, theme design, customization, plugin and more. Most Popular blog sites like BBC America, TechCrunch, Bloomberg and popular brands like Bata, Mozilla Blog, etc use WordPress. Thus, the demand for WordPress developers is high these days.

Why Choose WordPress Training at TOPS?

...

TOPS Technologies is the most popular and trusted training institute since 2008. If you want to develop your career as a WordPress developer, then join an in-depth WordPress Training Course by TOPS Technologies and gain knowledge and expertise in WordPress. Our experienced trainers will help you to understand and learn from the basics.

Practice assignments and Live Project Training will be provided during training classes to be confident about the platform. After successfully completion of course, you will get certification and job assurance with interview questions. After learning WordPress you can choose a career path as Web designer, developer, blogger, educator and more.

Sound good? Any question? You can tell us your questions or enroll via emailing us at inquiry@tops-int.com or visit your nearest TOPS Training center.
